Set oven control to broil. Separate bagels and place on large cookie sheets. Squeeze 1 teaspoon pizza sauce on each half. Dollop 1/2 teaspoon pesto sauce on each bagel half. Top each with 1 tablespoon cheese and 2 slices pepperoni. Broil with tops 4 to 6 inches from heat for 2 1/2 to 3 1/2 minutes or until cheese is melted. Serve at once.